  "body": "### Description\r\nNowadays we are using 2 boolean properties to manage **date and time format** in `src/app/global/local_account_sensitive_settings.nim`:\r\n- `isDDMMYYDateFormat`\r\n- `is24hTimeFormat`\r\n\r\nIt will improve the code if instead of using booleans, an enumerator is used so it is clear what happen in both cases, if true or if false and they can be prepared, as well, for future formats. \r\n\r\nSee comments on the following PR for more information:\r\n_Originally posted by @Khushboo-dev-cpp in https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/pull/5543#discussion_r865662961_\r\n",
